<h2>2. Purpose of the Tool</h2>
<p>
SmartCity SeqyTool v5.1 is an open-source diagnostic platform designed to evaluate and benchmark territorial and urban intelligence maturity for municipalities, public institutions, and academic users. 
The Tool is intended solely for educational, institutional, and research purposes, and must not be used for unlawful, discriminatory, or commercial exploitation.
</p>

